data.description: Everything you need on one floor! Beautiful NO-STEP ranch w/ 3 Bedrooms on 1st floor. Update Kitchen, New Appliances, MBA remodel, freshly painted, 2 full BA 1st floor. 2nd floor incl. a bonus room and bedroom-or extra storage. 1st floor laundry WBFP, remarkable landscaping, 2 patios, fish pond & fire pit. 2 car garage. Very close to St. Antoninus Church/School & shopping. Have your buyer think of all the possibilities. This home is just waiting for your finishing touches.
